interesting points: The sighting lasted only 20 seconds., The objects were described as bright and capable of instantaneous stops., No photographs were taken during the sighting., The objects were observed to flash on and off., The speed of the objects was determined to be fast, estimated around 60-45 mph.
witness description: No specific witnesses were detailed in the report.
